    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/a96a519fad2014ae443fe092fd4f6e44.poster.avif?t=1753839124\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/a96a519fad2014ae443fe092fd4f6e44.webm?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><u>怨念</u></strong>是一个双人合作，密室逃脱类型的游戏。以日本恐怖主题为背景，双方玩家需要合作探索揭秘完成游戏。<br>玩家是一对在现时代前往日本观光的旅客。在观光一座诡异的寺庙时，突然的一场地震使玩家跌落了幽暗的谷底。在那里玩家会看见一座荒废的豪宅。<br>玩家需要合作摸索这座古宅的秘密。在解密的同时也要幸存潜伏在每个走廊和空间的阴险怨灵。<br>你和队友被逼分开，所以双人必须沟通，壮胆，导航与合作逃离这座古城，重见光明。<br>玩家一定要和一位朋友一起体验这个双人合作的游戏<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/c88e6141402b44278b13fb4197184343.poster.avif?t=1753839124\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/c88e6141402b44278b13fb4197184343.webm?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><u>独特的故事和传说</u></strong><br>’怨念‘设有跨时代的独特故事情节，玩家会直接被带入谜底的中心。玩家会探索日本江户时代不同的场景，他们会在阴险的空间里遇到什么不可思议的结局呢？<br>游戏的故事元素，秘密，和场景人物将会从手绘的过场动画和人物互动中慢慢被揭示。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/05efad2bad5b4a1367926ddd2acf2e43.poster.avif?t=1753839124\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/05efad2bad5b4a1367926ddd2acf2e43.webm?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><u>充满气氛环境</u></strong><br>怨念构建了带有恐怖实感氛围和音效设计的场景，好让玩家可以沉浸在游戏世界当中。<br>游戏艺术混合了实景和虚构的设计，给玩家带来一种奇妙又诡异的感觉，让他们有梦幻般或噩梦般的体验。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/1a78653b3720f12df4a508d1ee7ac75a.poster.avif?t=1753839124\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/1a78653b3720f12df4a508d1ee7ac75a.webm?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/1a78653b3720f12df4a508d1ee7ac75a.mp4?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><u>挑战性的谜题</u></strong><br>玩家需要在游戏中破解各种谜题逃离地底的古宅。双人需要合作以逻辑思考，横向思维，解码解密的能力，甚至在典型的迷宫中寻找出路解密。<br>谜题是根据实景版的真人密室逃脱设计，可是我们在这里不需要被物理上限制。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/e836bf411c5d2f43da697dc0361cbf8d.poster.avif?t=1753839124\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/e836bf411c5d2f43da697dc0361cbf8d.webm?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/e836bf411c5d2f43da697dc0361cbf8d.mp4?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><u>双人合作</u></strong><br>怨念是一个双人合作的游戏体验，玩家需要和另一位朋友一起玩。有朋友的陪伴应该会增添一些安全感。你相信谁能够帮助你一起逃生呢？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/edd6704a14e81b274b1a0f56f6a46e0a.poster.avif?t=1753839124\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799220/extras/edd6704a14e81b274b1a0f56f6a46e0a.webm?t=1753839124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><u>3章节游戏内容</u></strong><br>怨念的游戏会有3个章节。每一章会有1个小时左右的游戏内容，恐怖氛围和探索解密。玩家会被带到江户时代的不同的场景探索解密。最后，他们会在阴险的空间里遇到什么不可思议的结局呢？<br><br><br><strong><u>现在开始售卖了。来试试看吧</u></strong>",
